basic.Peptide Name: Phlebotomus duboscqi defensin (PduDef; defensins; Insects, animals)
basic.Target Organism: Gram-positive bacteria:Staphylococcus aureus (MIC=0.78-1.56 µM), Aspergillus fumigatus (MIC=12.5-25 µM).Fungi:Fusarium culmorum (MIC=1.56-3.12 µM), Fusarium oxysporum (MIC=3.12-6.25 µM), Neurospora crassa (MIC=6.25-12.5 µM), Trichoderma viride (MIC=3.12-6.25 µM), Trichophyton mentagrophytes (MIC=25-50 µM), Candida albicans (MIC=6.25-12.5 µM), Saccharomyces cerevisiae (MIC=25-50 µM).Parasite:Leishmania major promastigote forms (IC50=68-85 µM).
